hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: How do I get an outside line? express rx drugstore shutting down 6% is not enough! shut it all down! defund everything including all gov’t contracts and contractors! defund all the services Obama and Michelle enjoy! shut down the congressional barbershop and all the other perks! cut off all aid to foreign gov’ts! defund the military industrial/intelligence complex! defund the NSA, TSA, CIA, FBI, DOJ, IRS, Secret Service, DHS, DEA, FDA, USDA, DOE, etc. If someone receives a federal paycheck directly or indirectly – cut them off! Bring our people home from all these wars and police actions/occupations!
